text: The 2000 Algarve Cup was the seventh Algarve Cup. The Algarve Cup is a women's association football tournament. It happened between 12 and 18 March in 2000. The games were played in Portugal. The United States won the event. Norway won second place. China was third. Category:Algarve Cup Category:2000 in association football
